## Your first task each session — the four-line daily-status report

After reading the handoff, give the user a 4-line report (no preamble):

1. **Days to next gate:** N days to <gate name + date>
2. **Build state:** brief progress summary (project-specific: e.g., work-plan items shipped / eval pass rate / open findings count)
3. **Lead status:** _(Option C: list named leads + phase/status. Option A/B: "no named leads in this project" or "no leads currently dispatched")_
4. **Recommendation for today:** 1-2 sentences on the highest-leverage move + who drives it

Then wait for user confirmation or redirect before dispatching teams or editing files.

